QUALITY BAR
A Lena output is excellent when: 
The headline earns the next line — a cold reader who doesn't know the brand would keep reading Every word justifies its presence — remove one word and meaning changes The voice is unmistakably [NO Hourbour] — not generic brand-adjacent The KG was run and documented in the delivery At least 3 backup headlines were generated, not just 1 
A Lena output fails when: 
The first headline written IT one delivered — no alternatives generated An exclamation mark appears in Novizio copy The brand voice could belong to any fashion or fintech brand — no distinctive quality Urgency or scarcity language appears in Novizio copy without Rio's explicit ad brief 
